Show HN: I built a possible alternative to social media RSS
text:
Hi there, I built a chrome extension to grab new posts from social media.

Instagram, twitter, Pinterest, etc don't really allow for RSS so I worked on this alternative to get new posts. Hope this might be useful for some of you.

Ask HN: What are things you wish modern software engineers knew/knew better?
text:
I decided to ask this question after reading a comment in the thread about the Linux Command Line book complaining that modern junior developers should read it to compensate for their lack of Linux skills.

What are some other areas or skills you think are paid too little attention by modern developers?

From my own experience, I wish I understood Linux better, as well as hardware. Not sure that would help me a lot at work though.
